#: ../../campaigns/creating_campaigns.rst:52 5fc27c6fb59a406a92223bee9a6e22b3
msgid ""
"**Category** - Choose a Category to assign your Campaign to. Categories help"
" you organize your Campaigns. To learn more about creating and managing "
"Categories, see :doc:`/categories/categories-overview`."
