#: ../../campaigns/creating_campaigns.rst:54 8b734fc2f32348cfb3435d13a4394997
msgid ""
"**Published** - Click the toggle switch to publish or un-publish the "
"Campaign. Ensure that you don't publish a Campaign until you're actually "
"ready for it to go live. You can also schedule to publish or un-publish a "
"Campaign at a future date by selecting a time and date."
msgstr ""

